body_html:
CC @mrry @guschmue any ideas?

AFAIK immintrin.h is a header file for intel SIMD intrinsics.
Maybe the compilation issues are related to VS2017 as we are not seeing them in our builds that use vs2015?
The files you edited should be specific to windows. We should be able to test if your changes are OK on older versions of VS (2015 update 3 is the only one we actually test on).
